data.description: Welcome to this LIKE-NEW home that is just 7 months old! Located in Cavins Farm, this home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a 1-car garage! Walk into the foyer to an open floor plan downstairs with the living room, dining area and kitchen with pantry closet. There is also a half bath for guests downstairs. Upstairs, the master bedroom boasts a large walk-in closet and full bathroom. You will also find the secondary bedrooms, laundry closet and the second full bathroom upstairs. Outside, enjoy the private, fenced-in backyard. In the summer, enjoy the COMMUNITY POOL just around the corner! All kitchen appliances, security system, blinds, PLUS the washer and dryer to convey with the home! Conveniently located minutes from I-26, downtown Woodruff, restaurants, shopping & near both Greenville and Spartanburg. Call to schedule your showing today!
